I would like to understand the step-by-step process for setting up the integration, including the necessary API key permissions You can reach me at janesmith@company.com.. Additionally, I would like to know how the integration can be customized to meet specific requirements My name is Omar Hassan.. Please provide a comprehensive guide or tutorial on how to successfully set up the integration with ActiveCampaign. I look forward to your prompt response. Thank you for your support.
